OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782492482
OL,3,CGovernment urged to compensate victims
OL,4,Cof mesh and sodium valproate scandals
OL,6,FThe government has been urged to make
OL,7,Fa decision on compensation for people
OL,8,Fwho have suffered avoidable harm from
OL,9,Fpelvic mesh and the epilepsy drug
OL,10,Fsodium valproate.
OL,12,FThe Hughes Report called for a two-
OL,13,Fstage redress scheme for patients
OL,14,Faffected by the medical products,
OL,15,Fwhich have caused debilitating pain
OL,16,Fand learning difficulties.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782492482
OL,3,CGovernment urged to compensate victims
OL,4,Cof mesh and sodium valproate scandals
OL,6,FThe report was published more than two
OL,7,Fyears ago, and its author, patient
OL,8,Fsafety commissioner for England,
OL,9,FProfessor Henrietta Hughes, has
OL,10,Fexpressed her disappointment over the
OL,11,F"continued absence of visible and
OL,12,Ftimely progress".
OL,14,FCampaigners also urged the government
OL,15,Fto act, saying compensation "is not
OL,16,Foptional and is long overdue".
OL,18,FTransvaginal mesh implants were used
OL,19,Fto treat pelvic organ prolapse and
OL,20,Fincontinence after childbirth between
OL,21,F1998 and 2020.
OL,26,@tD@PO]wD@]OUxD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782492482
OL,3,CGovernment urged to compensate victims
OL,4,Cof mesh and sodium valproate scandals
OL,6,FHowever, they have caused debilitating
OL,7,Fharm in some cases, leading to women
OL,8,Fhaving their bladders or bowels
OL,9,Fremoved.
OL,11,FThe NHS restricted the use of these
OL,12,Fimplants in 2018, and they are now
OL,13,Fused only as a last resort.
OL,15,FMeanwhile, thousands of babies are
OL,16,Fthought to have been harmed by sodium
OL,17,Fvalproate use during pregnancies since
OL,18,Fthe 1970s.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782492482
OL,3,CGovernment urged to compensate victims
OL,4,Cof mesh and sodium valproate scandals
OL,6,FThe drug, used to treat epilepsy and
OL,7,Fbipolar disorder, is now known to
OL,8,Fcause birth defects and lifelong
OL,9,Flearning difficulties and impacted an
OL,10,Festimated 20,000 families.
OL,12,FThe Hughes report had suggested
OL,13,Fvictims should start to receive
OL,14,Finterim compensation payments from
OL,15,F2025.
OL,17,FIt said an interim award of #25,000
OL,18,Fwas the "median amount patients said
OL,19,Fwould be appropriate".
OL,26,@zD@IOU{D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782492482
OL,3,CGovernment urged to compensate victims
OL,4,Cof mesh and sodium valproate scandals
OL,6,FHowever, Hughes said the government
OL,7,Fhas still not given a "substantive
OL,8,Fresponse" to her recommendations and
OL,9,Fshe has written to No 10 for more
OL,10,Finformation under the Medicines and
OL,11,FMedical Devices Act, with a deadline
OL,12,Ffor their response set for July 16.
OL,14,FThe Commissioner said: "Nearly two and
OL,15,Fa half years ago, the Hughes Report
OL,16,Fset out clear and urgent
OL,17,Frecommendations shaped by the
OL,18,Fexperience of patients harmed by
OL,19,Fvalproate and pelvic mesh and the
OL,20,Fsystemic failures that followed.
OL,26,@oD@WOUpD@IO]vD@XOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782492482
OL,3,CGovernment urged to compensate victims
OL,4,Cof mesh and sodium valproate scandals
OL,6,F"It provided compelling evidence of
OL,7,Fenduring gaps in recognition of harm,
OL,8,Faccess to redress, and the adequacy of
OL,9,Fsupport available to affected patients.
OL,11,F"These are not new concerns, but as
OL,12,Fthe Hughes Report highlighted, they
OL,13,Fcontinue to have significant
OL,14,Fconsequences for those who have been
OL,15,Fharmed and indeed continue to do so".
OL,17,FHughes said that the recommendations
OL,18,Fin the report are "direct and
OL,19,Factionable" and address the issues in
OL,20,F"how the system responds to harm".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
