PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782492482
OL,3,CGovernment urged to compensate victims
OL,4,Cof mesh and sodium valproate scandals
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FShe criticised the "continued absence
OL,12,Fof visible and timely progress" and
OL,13,Fsaid the lack of action risks
OL,14,Fperpetuating harm and was disappointed
OL,15,Fin the lack of government response.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
