FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782492482
OL,3,CGovernment urged to compensate victims
OL,4,Cof mesh and sodium valproate scandals
OL,6,FKath Sansom, founder of campaign group
OL,7,FSling the Mesh, said the "evidence has
OL,8,Fbeen undeniable about the thousands of
OL,9,Fwomen living with devastating,
OL,10,Firreversible injuries caused by
OL,11,Ftreatments they trusted".
OL,13,F"These women did everything right.
OL,14,FThey trusted their doctors. And for
OL,15,Fthat trust, they've paid with their
OL,16,Fhealth, their jobs, their savings, and
OL,17,Ffor some their marriages, but moreover
OL,18,Ftheir sense of self," she added.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUsD@XO]uD@AOUzD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782492482
OL,3,CGovernment urged to compensate victims
OL,4,Cof mesh and sodium valproate scandals
OL,6,FShe said that it was "not good enough"
OL,7,Fand stressed that women should not
OL,8,Fhave to "fight through the courts for
OL,9,Fjustice over a piece of plastic mesh
OL,10,Fthat has shattered their lives" and
OL,11,Fsaid that compensation is "not
OL,12,Foptional".
OL,14,FTom Shillito, health improvement and
OL,15,Fresearch manager at Epilepsy Action
OL,16,Fsaid is it "extremely worrying" that
OL,17,FProf Hughes is still pushing for
OL,18,Fanswers.
OL,26,@xD@LOUxD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782492482
OL,3,CGovernment urged to compensate victims
OL,4,Cof mesh and sodium valproate scandals
OL,6,F"For the families affected, this is
OL,7,Fnot about government process or policy
OL,8,Fdiscussions, it's about the reality of
OL,9,Fliving with the consequences of harm
OL,10,Fevery single day," he said.
OL,12,FHe highlighted that some families have
OL,13,Fwaited for "more than 40 years" and
OL,14,Fare concerned about who will provide
OL,15,Fcare for their children "when they no
OL,16,Flonger can".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
