OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782492482
OL,3,CGovernment urged to compensate victims
OL,4,Cof mesh and sodium valproate scandals
OL,6,FA spokesperson from the Department of
OL,7,FHealth and Social Care said: "We
OL,8,Frecognise the significant impact that
OL,9,Fsodium valproate and pelvic mesh have
OL,10,Fhad on people and their families.
OL,12,F"This is a complex issue and our
OL,13,Fpriority is to ensure any response is
OL,14,Ffair, balanced and sensitive to those
OL,15,Faffected.
OL,17,F"We are carefully considering the
OL,18,Frecommendations within the Hughes
OL,19,FReport, in collaboration with relevant
OL,20,Fdepartments, and we aim to provide an
OL,21,Fupdate in due course."
OL,26,@oD@^OUtD@AOUyD@AOU}D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
